(Chapter 1: Getting Started) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The PDF Viewer SDK is built with Kotlin.) Tj T*
(It uses PdfiumAndroid for native rendering.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Key Features:) Tj T*
(- Open PDF from file or byte array) Tj T*
(- Smooth vertical scrolling between pages) Tj T*
(- Pinch to zoom with quality re-rendering) Tj T*
(- Double tap to zoom in and out) Tj T*
(- Text search across all pages) Tj T*
(- Text selection and copy support) Tj T*
ET
endstream
