(Chapter 2: Architecture) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The SDK has these components:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. PdfDocument - Native PDF document wrapper) Tj T*
(2. PdfRenderer - Rendering coordinator with cache) Tj T*
(3. BitmapCache - LRU cache for page bitmaps) Tj T*
(4. ZoomableLayout - Pinch zoom and pan gestures) Tj T*
(5. PdfPageAdapter - RecyclerView adapter) Tj T*
(6. PDFView - Public API component) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(All rendering uses Kotlin Coroutines on IO threads.) Tj T*
ET
endstream
