(Chapter 3: Text Features) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Search: Type any word in the search bar.) Tj T*
(The SDK finds all occurrences across every page.) Tj T*
(Total match count is displayed instantly.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Copy: Tap the Aa button to show text overlay.) Tj T*
(Long press to select text with native handles.) Tj T*
(Selected text can be copied to clipboard.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The text extraction runs in background using PdfBox.) Tj T*
ET
