(Chapter 4: Performance) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(For best performance:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. Use file paths instead of InputStreams) Tj T*
(2. Cache size adapts to device RAM automatically) Tj T*
(3. Only visible pages are rendered at full resolution) Tj T*
(4. Nearby pages are prefetched for smooth scrolling) Tj T*
(5. Zoom quality is enhanced by re-rendering) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The SDK supports Android 8.0 and above.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Thank you for using the PDF Viewer SDK.) Tj T*
ET
